1. Vision in the V2MOM defines:
Solution : C. What you want to do or achieve

2. Methods in the V2MOM are:
Solution : D. Actions and steps to take to achieve your vision

3. When writing the Measures portion of your V2MOM, think about:
Solution : D. The way you know you've been successful

4. An example of a SMART measure is:
Solution : B. Increase market share by 20% in 2017
